<div aria-hidden="true" aria-describedby="example-dialog-01-description" aria-labelledby="example-dialog-01-title" data-c-dialog data-c-dialog-escapable data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01" data-c-padding="tb(2)" role="dialog">
    <div data-c-background="white(100)" data-c-radius="rounded" data-c-margin="bottom(2)">
        <div data-c-background="c1(100)" data-c-padding="tb(1) right(3) left(1)" data-c-border="bottom(thin, solid, black)">
            <h5 
                data-c-color="white" 
                data-c-font-size="h4" 
                id="example-dialog-01-title" 
                data-c-font-weight="bold"
                data-c-dialog-focus>Add a Skill</h5>
            <p data-c-color="white" data-c-font-size="h5" data-c-margin="top(.5)">Select a skill from the list and complete the information.</p>
            <button data-c-dialog-action="close" data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01" type="button">
                <span data-c-color="white" data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-font-size="h3">x</span>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div data-c-border="bottom(thin, solid, black)" data-c-padding="all(1)">
            <form id="example-dialog-01-description">
                <div data-c-grid="gutter(all, 1)">
                    <div 
                        data-c-input="select" 
                        data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                        <label for="SEL2">Select a Skill</label>
                        <span>Required</span>
                        <div>
                            <i class="material-icons">
                                arrow_drop_down
                            </i>
                            <select required id="SEL2">
                                <option disabled>Select a skill...</option>
                                <option>Organic Chemistry</option>
                                <option selected>Design Research</option>
                                <option>Database Architecture</option>
                                <option>Digital Marketing</option>
                                <option>Interior Design</option>
                                <option>User Interface Design</option>
                                <option>Policy Analysis</option>
                                <option>Public Speaking</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <span>This input has an error.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                    <p 
                        data-c-margin="top(.5)"
                        data-c-font-weight="bold">Defined as:</p>
                    <p data-c-margin="top(.25) bottom(1)">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec imperdiet hendrerit mauris vitae lacinia. Mauris sollicitudin porta lorem, et consequat ipsum. Nulla vel purus eu metus tristique tincidunt. Proin in fringilla ipsum, a fermentum quam. Praesent finibus massa urna, eu scelerisque mauris sodales nec.</p>
                </div>
                <div data-c-grid="gutter(all, 1)">
                    <div 
                        data-c-input="select" 
                        data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                        <label for="SEL3">Select Your Level in this Skill</label>
                        <span>Required</span>
                        <div>
                            <i class="material-icons">
                                arrow_drop_down
                            </i>
                            <select required id="SEL3">
                                <option disabled>Select a level...</option>
                                <option>Beginner</option>
                                <option selected>Intermediate</option>
                                <option>Advanced</option>
                                <option>Expert</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <span>This input has an error.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div 
                    data-c-input="textarea"
                    data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                    <label for="TA2">Please offer evidence of your level in this skill:</label>
                    <span>Required</span>
                    <div>
                        <textarea id="TA2" required placeholder="e.g. Describe how you've used this skill in previous experiences...">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec imperdiet hendrerit mauris vitae lacinia. Mauris sollicitudin porta lorem, et consequat ipsum. Nulla vel purus eu metus tristique tincidunt. Proin in fringilla ipsum, a fermentum quam. Praesent finibus massa urna, eu scelerisque mauris sodales nec.</textarea>
                    </div>
                    <span>This input has an error.</span>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div data-c-padding="all(1)">
            <div data-c-grid="gutter(all, 1) middle">
                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of2)">
                    <button data-c-button="outline(slow)" data-c-radius="rounded" data-c-dialog-action="close" data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01">
                        Cancel
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of2)" data-c-alignment="base(right)">
                    {# David: if and when you get to the point of hooking this part of the dialog up, you'll like want to use the button I've commented out instead of the anchor. I've used an anchor here to simulate saving and reloading the page with the fake data included here in the modal. #}
                    {# <button 
                        data-c-button="solid(go)" 
                        data-c-radius="rounded" 
                        data-c-dialog-action="close" 
                        data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01">
                        Save Skill
                    </button> #}
                    <a 
                        href="$ROOT/01-create-skill/created#newSkill" 
                        title="Save and submit this skill."
                        data-c-button="solid(go)" 
                        data-c-radius="rounded">Save Skill</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
